The iPayX FX Audit MCP server is a forensic tool designed to audit foreign exchange transactions, detect hidden bank markups, and generate FINTRAC-certified reports [1][2]. It functions as a rail-agnostic layer for B2B payments across platforms like SWIFT, SEPA, and stablecoins [1][2].

To integrate it, add the server to your MCP client configuration using the endpoint URL `https://mcp.ipayx.ai/mcp` [3].

Example configuration:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "ipayx-fx": {
      "url": "https://mcp.ipayx.ai/mcp"
    }
  }
}
```

Key tools include `audit_fx_transaction` and `check_fx_mid_market_rate` [4][5].
